description.en: A world heritage protection and development DAO (Decentralized Autonomous Organization) accelerator, TemDAO funds and supports future builders in world heritage decentralized through DAOs working on a range of areas and infrastructure projects. TemDAO provides a launchpad, resources, mentorship, a shared network, and a suite of legal and smart contracts for DAOs.Our goal is to enable all world heritage and other tourism attractions to utilize IP-NFTs to fund, govern, and develop intellectual property worldwide, catalyzing a Cambrian explosion of digital IP assets.
